    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/f2236666fbb9206e9e257628b42c2029.avif?t=1749251789\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras_big/f2236666fbb9206e9e257628b42c2029.avif?t=1749251789 width=800 height=284 /></span><strong>Begin</strong> the mystery with the first two chapters in this Allogloom demo! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In this point and click adventure</strong> join Nora on her journey of weird and wonderful discovery. Uncover secrets and discover the truth to bring the residents of her town back home. With a note instructing her to go somewhere forbidden as her only hope. She now must explore what remains of Gruesome Grove and beyond to get to the bottom of the mystery. Why did monsters steal the residents and where did they come from?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/97dee0d62b342c82879589ee0bd34f7a.avif?t=1749251789\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras_big/97dee0d62b342c82879589ee0bd34f7a.avif?t=1749251789 width=800 height=97 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/b03d73a09de65809e6e51047898f7181.poster.avif?t=1749251789\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/b03d73a09de65809e6e51047898f7181.webm?t=1749251789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/0851bff67e6aaa89bd10d2e168715892.avif?t=1749251789\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras_big/0851bff67e6aaa89bd10d2e168715892.avif?t=1749251789 width=800 height=85 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First two chapters of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 40 minutes of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine items and negotiate with characters to solve interesting puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras/554bd8afe19a546e289c52255f8d74c2.avif?t=1749251789\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171410/extras_big/554bd8afe19a546e289c52255f8d74c2.avif?t=1749251789 width=800 height=296 /></span></p>",
